sequenceDiagram
    participant HA as Home Assistant (Modbus TCP Client)
    participant Proxy as modbus-proxy (asyncio server)
    participant Device as Modbus Device (TCP / RTU over TCP / RTU Serial)

    HA->>Proxy: TCP or RTU-over-TCP request
    activate Proxy
    Note right of Proxy: handle_client -> Client.read() (auto-detect)
    Proxy->>Proxy: Client._read() (detect TCP/RTU-over-TCP)
    Proxy->>Proxy: _transform_request(request, client_format)
    Note right of Proxy: ModBus._transform_request (remap unit id, add/remove CRC, MBAP header)
    Proxy->>Device: send transformed request (TCP or RTU)
    activate Device
    Device-->>Proxy: device reply
    deactivate Device
    Proxy->>Proxy: _transform_reply(reply, client_format)
    Proxy->>HA: reply (in requested format)
    deactivate Proxy
